premise_source_doc_sentence: The series is the second spin-off of a Disney Channel series  (  after the short-lived That 's So Raven spinoff Cory in the House  )  ; as well as the last Disney Channel series to debut broadcasting exclusively in standard definition , and the first of three Disney Channel shows to transition from standard definition to high definition , which occurred on August 7 , 2009 with the season 2 premiere , `` The Spy Who Shoved Me , '' and the third multi-camera comedy  (  after Sonny with a Chance and Jonas  )  to utilize a filmized appearance instead of the Filmlook appearance that was used in the first season .
